    <div class="section">
      <h2>📌 What is WayPrint?</h2>
      <p><strong>WayPrint</strong> is a premium, modern <em>Print-on-Demand</em> platform designed specifically for the Uzbekistan market. Users can upload custom designs, select high-quality T-shirts and products, and get them delivered nationwide. Inspired by global services like Printify, WayPrint is tailored for our region with speed, simplicity, and a beautiful UI.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🎯 Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>User-Friendly Design Upload</li>
        <li>Product Customization Options</li>
        <li>Real-Time Design Preview</li>
        <li>Secure Order and Delivery</li>
        <li>Admin Dashboard for Full Control</li>
        <li>Premium Branding and UX</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>⚙️ Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> React.js + Next.js + TailwindCSS</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> NestJS (TypeScript)</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL + Prisma</li>
        <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Cloudinary or AWS S3</li>
        <li><strong>Auth:</strong> JWT + Email Verification</li>
        <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Global, user-specific, or course-based</li>
        <li><strong>AI Features:</strong> Smart quiz & vocab (future)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🚧 Development Status</h2>
      <p>Currently under active development. MVP includes basic product flow, admin panel, order system, and secure file uploads.</p>
